*coreboot-1.4.5 (07 Apr 2010)

  07 Apr 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> +coreboot-1.4.5.ebuild:
  bug fix release for liveCDs.

*coreboot-1.4.4 (02 Apr 2010)

  02 Apr 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> +coreboot-1.4.4.ebuild:
  bug fix release for grub.

*coreboot-1.4.3 (01 Apr 2010)

  01 Apr 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> +coreboot-1.4.3.ebuild:
  Bug fix release that should resolve some outstanding bugs related to 
  grub-legacy support.

*coreboot-1.4.2 (16 Mar 2010)

  16 Mar 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> +coreboot-1.4.2.ebuild:
  Maintenance/doc update release.

*coreboot-1.4.1 (11 Mar 2010)

  11 Mar 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> +coreboot-1.4.1.ebuild:
  new version for unstable that works correctly with new grub-legacy-0.97-r11,
  which uses /boot/grub-legacy/ as the grub.conf dir. This pkg should move
  to stable in sync with sys-boot/grub-legacy-0.97-r11

*coreboot-1.4 (25 Feb 2010)

  25 Feb 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> +coreboot-1.4.ebuild:
  new non-beta release.

